docs {
  # SENG365 Travel Blog API Bruno Test Collection
  This collection is provided for you to test your API against as you implement the assignment. This collection is a **subset** of the final collection that your API will be marked against.
  
  Each folder of requests is self-contained and will reload the database to the default state before testing a specific endpoint, the order of the requests within a folder matters as some requests may depend on earlier ones _(tests may behave unexpectedly if you change the order of or remove requests)_.
  
  You are encouraged to add additional requests to test that your API functions as described, if you are ever unsure of the functionality expected run the request against the reference server using the `deployed` environment. However be warned that automatic updates may be made to the collection through git if issues are found. If you find any errors or inconsistencies with the collection and the reference server provided please reach out to Morgan English (morgan.english@canterbury.ac.nz).
}
